arStrings.szText: Heart of Mold
As desperation grows, a more effective remedy for gut rot is needed.
Yolanda has asked me to take the head of the most recent hunter trophy nailed to the gate of Wejinhani. It should make a suitable offering to Zurke, the witch.
Take the head from the Grotesque Trophy
I must travel to the clearing in the Corpsewail Deluge where I hope to commune with the witch Zurke.
Find the clearing in the Corpsewail Deluge
I have made the offering and lit the torches. Now I must speak with the witch Zurke.
Speak with Zurke
I should speak to Yolanda about the next steps of how to treat gut rot. She seems to have gotten worse.
Speak with Yolanda
Zurke has asked me to slay a snake known as Nuroth the Vile Fang. Once I kill him, I need to take his eye and return to Zurke.
Slay Nuroth the Vile Fang and claim his {ITEM}
I must travel to the clearing in the Corpsewail Deluge where I hope to commune with the witch Zurke. I should place the offering and light the nearby torches.
Place the Grotesque Head in the Offering Bowl
Light the Mossy Torches: {DONE_OVER_NEEDED}
Zurke has asked me to place the eye in the animal corpse he has provided. I should have a cure after the animal reacts.
Place the Oversized Snake Eyes
Zurke has given me a moldy heart and instructed me to return to Wejinhani to heal those suffering from gut rot. I hope Yolanda has enough time for the remedy to help.
Bring the Heart of Mold to Yolanda
Zurke has asked me to slay a snake known as Nuroth the Vile Fang. Once I kill him, I need to take his eye and return to Zurke.
Return to Zurke
Zurke has asked me to place the eye in the animal corpse he has provided. I should have a cure after the animal reacts.
Take the {ITEM}
